  "title": "Senior Building Electrician",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Duties & Responsibilities for Senior building electrician</strong></u></p><p>·  Installing and maintaining, repairing building electrical&\nmechanical distribution systems</p><p>·   Monitor the operations and make customer approved adjustments of\nchilled water systems, heat exchangers, CRAC Units, HVAC, electrical systems,emergency back-up systems, hot water systems, pumps, valves, filters and other\nmechanical and electrical equipment</p><p>·  Installing outlets, disconnects, motor starters, inside and\noutside lighting systems, frequency drives, building safety equipment, fans,pumps, and motors, and other electrical-related systems, fire alarm systems</p><p>·  Maintain and repair the mechanical, electrical, security and fire\nprotection systems that protect and support business critical information\nsystems (servers, mainframes, etc)</p><p>·  working understanding of commercial three phase electrical\nsystems</p><p>· Disassemble, clean, repair, and reassemble a variety of electrical\nappliances, controls and equipment following established procedures</p><p>· Diagnose and correct malfunctions in interior and exterior\nelectrical circuits</p><p>· Test electrical equipment to identify and fix malfunctions</p><p>· Assist with job site and general safety, including general ground\nsupport, staging materials, and general site preparation and clean-up.</p><p>·  Ensure that all equipment stays in line with electrical codes,\nregulations, and standards</p><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><p>Diploma/Or equivalent\nand 2 years of experience in maintenance/repair or related field; or any\nequivalent combination of education, training, and experience.</p><p>1.    Two (2) years of HVAC experience preferably\nworking with chilled water systems, or a combination of training and work experience.</p><p>2.Proficient in providing Building Services technical advice.</p><p>3. Familiar with HVAC and building codes and standards</p><p>4.  Extensive experience working across a variety of building\nprojects associated to industrial, commercial.</p>",
